refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
&style.oop;
public DateTimeDateTime::setTime inthour intminute intsecond0
&style.procedural;
DateTimedate_time_set DateTimeobject inthour intminute intsecond0
Redefine o horário atual do objeto DateTime para um diferente.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Examplo do método DateTime::setTime

&style.oop;


<?php
$date = new DateTime('2001-01-01');

$date->setTime(14, 55);
echo $date->format('Y-m-d H:i:s') . "\n";

$date->setTime(14, 55, 24);
echo $date->format('Y-m-d H:i:s') . "\n";
?>



&style.procedural;


<?php
$date = date_create('2001-01-01');

date_time_set($date, 14, 55);
echo date_format($date, 'Y-m-d H:i:s') . "\n";

date_time_set($date, 14, 55, 24);
echo date_format($date, 'Y-m-d H:i:s') . "\n";
?>


   &examples.outputs.similar;


2001-01-01 14:55:00
2001-01-01 14:55:24




   Valores que excedem os limites são adicionados aos seus valores anteriores


<?php
$date = new DateTime('2001-01-01');

$date->setTime(14, 55, 24);
echo $date->format('Y-m-d H:i:s') . "\n";

$date->setTime(14, 55, 65);
echo $date->format('Y-m-d H:i:s') . "\n";

$date->setTime(14, 65, 24);
echo $date->format('Y-m-d H:i:s') . "\n";

$date->setTime(25, 55, 24);
echo $date->format('Y-m-d H:i:s') . "\n";
?>


   &example.outputs;


2001-01-01 14:55:24
2001-01-01 14:56:05
2001-01-01 15:05:24
2001-01-02 01:55:24
